003892BF.desc: Your Shadow damage over time effects have a {c_number}[{SF_0}*100|%x|]{/c} chance to deal {c_number}[{SF_1}*100|%x|]{/c} bonus damage each time they deal damage. This chance is increased by {c_number}[{SF_2}*100|%x|]{/c} and bonus damage is increased by {c_number}[{SF_3}*100|1%x|]{/c} for each {c_number}[{SF_4}]{/c} Willpower you have.
